{
  "stem": "18581.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 352.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I spoke to them as if I was a Lithuanian youth escaping from the Nazis who wanted to send me to forced labor in Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the way I spoke, they could not recognize I was not Jewish, because their Lithuanian was not as pure as mine.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I spoke with a northwestern accent, [NON-ENGLISH], which is practically impossible to-- to copy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I found out that it was quiet in Vilna ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After many murders and so on, it was quiet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And since I had no other place-- and there was also I had a-- an unexpected meeting with a young girl who used to be a waitress in Vilna in [INAUDIBLE] restaurant, where my Lithuanian co-workers and I used to eat lunch.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a dairy restaurant, very good, called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she saw me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I wasn't sure whether she knew that-- she recognized me and I spoke to her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I wasn't sure whether she knew that I was Jewish, because I used to come to this restaurant during the Lithuanian rule and afterward during the Russian, with a bunch of 10 Lithuanians, men and women.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we all worked for the passport department and then for others.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she- I wasn't sure whether she knew I was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somewhere about 70, 80 kilometers from Vilna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not only she, but farmers who-- with whom I traded some.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I bought some bread and I paid them with a local currency and so on, or with something else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I heard from the farmers, who said-- some of them said, oh, we were in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went out near the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing special.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is a-- there is a gate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There is a Lithuanian policeman and a-- a ghetto policeman.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
